# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:56
translate spanish izzy10_d0995620:

    # "I pull back out onto the streets and start driving over towards Izzy's house."
    "Vuelvo a la calle y empiezo a conducir hacia la casa de Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:57
translate spanish izzy10_541c797d:

    # "Izzy in jail. Man, that sucks. I wonder if I'll ever even see her again?"
    "Izzy en la cárcel. Tío, qué asco. Me pregunto si la volveré a ver alguna vez."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:60
translate spanish izzy10_0161d2d8:

    # "At her house, I find the door unlocked. I open it and walk inside."
    "En su casa, veo que la puerta está abierta. La abro y entro."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:61
translate spanish izzy10_0d5bc151:

    # pc "Hello? Anybody home?"
    pc "¿Hola? ¿Hay alguien en casa?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:62
translate spanish izzy10_735aa81f:

    # "I can hear the television playing in the living room."
    "Oigo la televisión en el salón."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:65
translate spanish izzy10_48d7389b:

    # "Then two boys who must be Izzy's little brothers rush out."
    "Entonces salen corriendo dos chicos que deben de ser los hermanos pequeños de Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:66
translate spanish izzy10_c3511125:

    # "Older Boy" "Who are you? You better get out of our house!"
    "Older Boy" "¿Quién eres? ¡Más te vale salir de nuestra casa!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:67
translate spanish izzy10_a66a8306:

    # pc "Woah, calm down. I'm one of Izzy's friends. She's going to be uh... late."
    pc "Eh, tranquilos. Soy una amiga de Izzy. Va a llegar... tarde."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:68
translate spanish izzy10_807e3ac4:

    # pc "Your auntie is supposed to be coming, but Izzy wanted me to come sit with you until she gets here."
    pc "Se supone que va a venir vuestra tía, pero Izzy quería que viniera a haceros compañía hasta que llegue."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:71
translate spanish izzy10_1d52908f:

    # "Younger Boy" "Izzy? Who's that?"
    "Younger Boy" "¿Izzy? ¿Quién es esa?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:72
translate spanish izzy10_ecf25c52:

    # "Older Boy" "That's sis, dummy. That's what her friends call her."
    "Older Boy" "Es mi hermana, tonto. Así la llaman sus amigos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:73
translate spanish izzy10_9e4c4b50:

    # "Younger Boy" "Oh yeah!"
    "Younger Boy" "¡Ah, sí!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:74
translate spanish izzy10_380c7fa4:

    # "Older Boy" "Okay, you can come sit and watch TV with us, but if you try anything, we'll bust you."
    "Older Boy" "Vale, puedes venir a sentarte a ver la tele con nosotros, pero si intentas algo, te daremos una paliza."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:75
translate spanish izzy10_94570d10:

    # pc "All right then."
    pc "De acuerdo, entonces."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:78
translate spanish izzy10_be6441de:

    # "I go in and sit on the couch, while they sit on the floor in front of the coffee table, doing homework and watching cartoons on the television."
    "Entro y me siento en el sofá, mientras ellos se sientan en el suelo delante de la mesita, haciendo los deberes y viendo dibujos animados en la televisión."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:79
translate spanish izzy10_98c4afdf:

    # "After sitting for a couple minutes in awkward silence, the older boy turns towards me."
    "Después de estar sentados un par de minutos en un silencio incómodo, el chico mayor se gira hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:82
translate spanish izzy10_b0063ead:

    # "Older Boy" "What's your name?"
    "Older Boy" "¿Cómo te llamas?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:83
translate spanish izzy10_784c18d8:

    # pc "[pcname]. What's yours?"
    pc "[pcname]. ¿Y tú?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:84
translate spanish izzy10_ceb1abab:

    # "Older Boy" "I'm Paul. My brother is Stanley."
    "Older Boy" "Soy Paul. Mi hermano es Stanley."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:85
translate spanish izzy10_70696046:

    # pc "Nice to meet you both."
    pc "Encantada de conoceros a los dos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:86
translate spanish izzy10_3a7290ac:

    # "Paul" "So, are you one of her boyfriends?"
    "Paul" "Entonces, ¿eres uno de sus novios?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:87
translate spanish izzy10_2d34af9e:

    # "Paul" "Sis has lots of boyfriends, but she usually doesn't let us meet them."
    "Paul" "Mi hermana tiene muchos novios, pero normalmente no nos deja conocerlos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:88
translate spanish izzy10_fc1855ec:

    # pc "Yeah, I guess I am. We're friends."
    pc "Sí, supongo que sí. Somos amigos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:89
translate spanish izzy10_0b6b2f16:

    # "Stanley" "Where is she? Why isn't she at home?"
    "Stanley" "¿Dónde está? ¿Por qué no está en casa?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:92
translate spanish izzy10_e562930a:

    # pc "Well, the police arrested her. She might be going to jail."
    pc "Bueno, la policía la ha detenido. Puede que vaya a la cárcel."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:93
translate spanish izzy10_9d4dc068:

    # "Paul" "Oh. Like mom."
    "Paul" "Oh. Como mamá."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:94
translate spanish izzy10_363102ed:

    # "Stanley" "So we'll never see her again?"
    "Stanley" "¿Entonces no la volveremos a ver nunca más?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:95
translate spanish izzy10_05948c06:

    # "Paul" "Right."
    "Paul" "Exacto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:96
translate spanish izzy10_db875c8c:

    # pc "I wouldn't say that. We'll just have to wait to see what happens."
    pc "Yo no diría eso. Tendremos que esperar a ver qué pasa."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:97
translate spanish izzy10_f0cc05be:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, okay."
    "Paul" "Sí, vale."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:98
translate spanish izzy10_9054da2b:

    # "Stanley" "I don't want sis to go to jail."
    "Stanley" "No quiero que mi hermana vaya a la cárcel."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:100
translate spanish izzy10_8c26bb19:

    # pc "She just got busy with something, but she'll be home soon."
    pc "Solo se ha entretenido con algo, pero volverá a casa pronto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:101
translate spanish izzy10_aed5f95e:

    # "Paul" "Really? She's always here when we get off the bus. What'd she get busy with?"
    "Paul" "¿En serio? Siempre está aquí cuando bajamos del autobús. ¿Con qué se ha entretenido?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:102
translate spanish izzy10_0d6ab269:

    # pc "Just some stuff she had to do."
    pc "Solo con algunas cosas que tenía que hacer."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:103
translate spanish izzy10_f0cc05be_1:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, okay."
    "Paul" "Sí, vale."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:104
translate spanish izzy10_5c971f07:

    # "We go back to awkward silence for a few more minutes."
    "Volvemos al silencio incómodo durante unos minutos más."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:107
translate spanish izzy10_d9654c38:

    # "Stanley" "Do you know how to do your multiplication tables?"
    "Stanley" "¿Sabes hacer las tablas de multiplicar?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:108
translate spanish izzy10_c0dfc38d:

    # pc "Uh, yeah I do."
    pc "Eh, sí, las sé."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:109
translate spanish izzy10_5a2c5982:

    # "Stanley" "Could you help me with my homework then? I don't understand this stuff."
    "Stanley" "¿Me podrías ayudar con los deberes entonces? No entiendo esto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:110
translate spanish izzy10_e85ea253:

    # pc "Sure, let me see what you have there."
    pc "Claro, déjame ver qué tienes ahí."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:113
translate spanish izzy10_b17956ae:

    # "Stanley gets up and sits on the couch next to me, putting his worksheet and book on his lap to show me."
    "Stanley se levanta y se sienta en el sofá a mi lado, poniendo la hoja de ejercicios y el libro en su regazo para enseñármelo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:114
translate spanish izzy10_b975883b:

    # "Stanley" "I know that 8 plus 6 is 14. But this says that 8 times 6 is 48. How the heck does that work?"
    "Stanley" "Sé que 8 más 6 son 14. Pero aquí dice que 8 por 6 son 48. ¿Cómo diablos funciona eso?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:115
translate spanish izzy10_329fcf1a:

    # pc "So you know how to do addition? 8 plus 8?"
    pc "¿Entonces sabes sumar? ¿8 más 8?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:116
translate spanish izzy10_04dda5a7:

    # "Stanley" "Yeah."
    "Stanley" "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:117
translate spanish izzy10_1c11dbdd:

    # pc "Well think of multiplication like you're doing addition over and over again."
    pc "Bueno, piensa en la multiplicación como si estuvieras sumando una y otra vez."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:118
translate spanish izzy10_b949eaf3:

    # pc "Here, write 8 six times on your paper. Eight six times is eight times six."
    pc "Toma, escribe 8 seis veces en tu papel. Ocho seis veces es ocho por seis."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:119
translate spanish izzy10_b115a24b:

    # "Stanley" "Oh, I get it."
    "Stanley" "Ah, ya lo pillo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:120
translate spanish izzy10_8b68d233:

    # pc "Then put a plus between each of those 8's and add them all together."
    pc "Entonces pon un signo más entre cada uno de esos 8 y súmalos todos juntos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:121
translate spanish izzy10_e6a0ee82:

    # "He starts adding, writing the number above each of the eights on his page until he reaches the last one that is 48."
    "Empieza a sumar, escribiendo el número encima de cada uno de los ochos en su hoja hasta llegar al último, que es 48."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:122
translate spanish izzy10_7d468f4d:

    # "Stanley" "I get it! Wow, you should be a teacher."
    "Stanley" "¡Ya lo pillo! Vaya, deberías ser profesor."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:125
translate spanish izzy10_d3d886b1:

    # "I hear the front door open and a woman's voice calls out."
    "Oigo que se abre la puerta principal y una voz de mujer llama."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:126
translate spanish izzy10_e6d98dc8:

    # "Woman" "Boys? Y'all in here?"
    "Woman" "¿Chicos? ¿Estáis todos aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:129
translate spanish izzy10_e3c838b3:

    # "The woman, who must be the boy's auntie, walks around the corner and both of them rush up to hug her."
    "La mujer, que debe de ser la tía del chico, dobla la esquina y los dos corren a abrazarla."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:130
translate spanish izzy10_ec0adf9c:

    # "Auntie" "Everything okay here?"
    "Auntie" "¿Todo bien por aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:131
translate spanish izzy10_5e4c7b42:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, we're all good."
    "Paul" "Sí, todo va bien."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:132
translate spanish izzy10_60d1cbf2:

    # "Stanley" "[pcname] was teaching me how to do my times table."
    "Stanley" "[pcname] me estaba enseñando a hacer las tablas de multiplicar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:133
translate spanish izzy10_ad65d7e3:

    # "Auntie" "That's nice of him."
    "Auntie" "Qué detalle por su parte."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:134
translate spanish izzy10_31976fc3:

    # "Auntie" "You two go to your room and pack up some clothes. You're going to come stay at my house for a few days, okay?"
    "Auntie" "Id a vuestra habitación y preparad algo de ropa. Os vais a quedar en mi casa unos días, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:135
translate spanish izzy10_32e2b2bb:

    # "Paul" "Is sis okay?"
    "Paul" "¿Está bien mi hermana?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:136
translate spanish izzy10_d6e45f9a:

    # "Auntie" "She's okay, but she's going to be gone for a bit."
    "Auntie" "Está bien, pero va a estar fuera un tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:137
translate spanish izzy10_e67935e5:

    # "Stanley" "How long?"
    "Stanley" "¿Cuánto tiempo?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:138
translate spanish izzy10_1f41c1ac:

    # "Auntie" "I don't know yet honey. Go pack your bags, okay?"
    "Auntie" "Aún no lo sé, cariño. Id a hacer las maletas, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:141
translate spanish izzy10_3581e151:

    # "The two boys run off towards their rooms, and I stand up to talk to their auntie."
    "Los dos niños salen corriendo hacia sus habitaciones y yo me levanto para hablar con su tía."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:142
translate spanish izzy10_f78cee83:

    # "Auntie" "Thanks for coming over and sitting with them for a bit."
    "Auntie" "Gracias por venir y quedarte un rato con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:143
translate spanish izzy10_5301b871:

    # pc "Oh, no problem. They seem like good kids."
    pc "Oh, no hay problema. Parecen buenos chicos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:144
translate spanish izzy10_bd9c1d85:

    # "Auntie" "They are. I wish they didn't have to go through all this. First their mom, now their sister."
    "Auntie" "Lo son. Ojalá no tuvieran que pasar por todo esto. Primero su madre, ahora su hermana."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:145
translate spanish izzy10_8a42d1af:

    # pc "Is she going to be okay?"
    pc "¿Se va a poner bien?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:146
translate spanish izzy10_74736fd1:

    # "Auntie" "She had a lot of drugs on her when they arrested her and that other boy. She has a couple of priors as well. It doesn't look good."
    "Auntie" "Llevaba muchas drogas encima cuando la arrestaron a ella y a ese otro chico. Además, tiene un par de antecedentes. No pinta bien."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:147
translate spanish izzy10_139f3015:

    # "Auntie" "I've been trying to get her to drop the drugs for a long time."
    "Auntie" "Llevo mucho tiempo intentando que deje las drogas."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:148
translate spanish izzy10_5e1c08a1:

    # "Auntie" "But it's hard to take care of two kids with a minimum wage job. Isabel didn't ask for any of this either."
    "Auntie" "Pero es difícil cuidar de dos niños con un trabajo con el salario mínimo. Isabel tampoco pidió nada de esto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:149
translate spanish izzy10_847af3a0:

    # "Auntie" "I don't know how {i}I'm{/i} even going to take care of these boys."
    "Auntie" "No sé ni cómo {i}voy{/i} a cuidar de estos chicos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:150
translate spanish izzy10_45975e4c:

    # "Auntie" "But, I'll figure it out. Got no other choice."
    "Auntie" "Pero ya se me ocurrirá algo. No tengo otra opción."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:151
translate spanish izzy10_527206cb:

    # "Auntie" "Anyways, thanks again. I'll take it from here."
    "Auntie" "En fin, gracias de nuevo. A partir de aquí me encargo yo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:154
translate spanish izzy10_47574532:

    # "She walks me towards the front door, but before I leave, Paul and Stanley come back out."
    "Me acompaña hasta la puerta principal, pero antes de que me vaya, Paul y Stanley vuelven a salir."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:155
translate spanish izzy10_82761cf4:

